%{k%~%~%}:0 | %{k%~%~%}:' <= _ \[ Gradations:0 | WordBoundary ]* %{D%}:0 \[ %{AV%+%}: | WordBoundary ]* [ %{AV%-%}: \[ WordBoundary ]* %{AV%+%}: ]* [ WordBoundary ] ;

